    "11192073": {
      "title": "Platform effect on RFID tag antennas and co-design considerations",
      "abstract": "In this paper, an UHF tag antenna is demonstrated to be co-designed with a plastic Sushi plate to achieve the conjugate impedance matching between the antenna and the ASIC. The reading range of the RFID system using such co-designed tag is greatly enhanced."
